OL,3,CTravis Perkins fined #2m after dad-of-
OL,4,Cthree killed by timber-load lorry fall
OL,6,FA major building supplies firm has
OL,7,Fbeen fined #2 million after a "grossly
OL,8,Finadequate and unsafe" timber load
OL,9,Ffell from a lorry and killed a dad-of-
OL,10,Fthree in an oncoming car.
OL,12,FJack Stevens, 28, was driving his BMW
OL,13,Fwhen materials pierced his windscreen
OL,14,Fand killed him on the A26 in Newhaven,
OL,15,FEast Sussex on May 13 2020.
OL,17,FTravis Perkins Trading Company Limited
OL,18,Fpleaded guilty to three offences under
OL,19,Fhealth and safety laws in November
OL,20,Flast year.
