OL,3,CTravis Perkins fined #2m after dad-of-
OL,4,Cthree killed by timber-load lorry fall
OL,6,FProsecutor Richard Heller told Hove
OL,7,FCrown Court on Thursday that the
OL,8,Fbusiness, said to be the largest in
OL,9,Fthe UK operating around 600 outlets,
OL,10,Fadmitted a breach of general duty and
OL,11,Ftwo regulatory breaches over the fatal
OL,12,Fincident.
OL,14,FAt the sentencing hearing, footage
OL,15,Fshowed the moment the timber came
OL,16,Floose and hit Mr Stevens' car and fell
OL,17,Facross the road.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/12
