OL,3,CTravis Perkins fined #2m after dad-of-
OL,4,Cthree killed by timber-load lorry fall
OL,6,FMr Heller said further footage not
OL,7,Fshown in court also captured "other
OL,8,Froad users being visibly shocked upon
OL,9,Flooking into the car".
OL,11,FA review of how the timber load was
OL,12,Fsecured was carried out by the Health
OL,13,Fand Safety Executive concluded "the
OL,14,Fsecurity of the load was grossly
OL,15,Finadequate and unsafe from the point
OL,16,Fof entering the public road network",
OL,17,Fthe court heard.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/12
