OL,3,CTravis Perkins fined #2m after dad-of-
OL,4,Cthree killed by timber-load lorry fall
OL,6,FIt added that the incident was
OL,7,F"entirely foreseeable and preventable"
OL,8,Fwith proper planning and practices in
OL,9,Fplace after the mass of six timbers
OL,10,Fand other materials was secured with
OL,11,Fan "insufficient" single strap.
OL,13,FThe court heard the load had been
OL,14,Fchecked by the driver and another
OL,15,Femployee before leaving the company's
OL,16,Fsite in Newhaven at around 7:30am.
OL,18,FBut according to company policy, the
OL,19,Florry should have been checked by a
OL,20,Fmember of branch management staff,
OL,21,Fwhich the assisting employee was not.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/12
