OL,3,CTravis Perkins fined #2m after dad-of-
OL,4,Cthree killed by timber-load lorry fall
OL,6,FMr Heller added: "The prosecution
OL,7,Fasserts that the load was unsafe due
OL,8,Fto inadequate training of staff in
OL,9,Fload security, compounded by a failure
OL,10,Fto ensure proper procedures were being
OL,11,Fobserved to prevent an accident of
OL,12,Fthis kind occurring."
OL,14,FThe parents of Mr Stevens, who was a
OL,15,Fmanager at B&Q, sat in court as it was
OL,16,Fheard the couple suffered from
OL,17,F"extreme anxiety" since their son's
OL,18,Fdeath.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/12
