OL,4,Cthree killed by timber-load lorry fall
OL,6,FImposing the #2 million fine on Travis
OL,7,FPerkins, Judge Christine Henson KC
OL,8,Fsaid: "This was a tragedy that could
OL,9,Fand should have been avoided.
OL,11,F"Travis Perkins would have been aware
OL,12,Fof their health and safety obligations
OL,13,Fand how they should have been
OL,14,Ffulfilled.
OL,16,F"The defendant company failed in this
OL,17,Fregard."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/12
