OL,4,Cthree killed by timber-load lorry fall
OL,6,FBut the judge took into account
OL,7,F"proactive" steps made by the company
OL,8,Fsince Mr Stevens' death to improve
OL,9,Fsafety.
OL,11,FDefending the company, Kate Brunner KC
OL,12,Fmade a full apology to the family over
OL,13,Fthe incident which the company takes
OL,14,F"full responsibility" for.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/12
