OL,3,CTravis Perkins fined #2m after dad-of-
OL,4,Cthree killed by timber-load lorry fall
OL,6,F"The significant failures, which there
OL,7,Fwere, have been recognised and owned
OL,8,Fand acted upon by the company in the
OL,9,Ffullest way possible and that reflects
OL,10,Fthe seriousness the company takes a
OL,11,Ftragic incident of this kind," Ms
OL,12,FBrunner said.
OL,14,FShe told the court how the builders'
OL,15,Fmerchant has "driven industry-wide
OL,16,Fimprovements" on safety and rolled out
OL,17,Fnew training and a "robust system" for
OL,18,Fspot-checking through CCTV and
OL,19,Fpaperwork to make sure load safety
OL,20,Fmeasures are done properly.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/12
