OL,4,Cthree killed by timber-load lorry fall
OL,6,F"Our family is still finding it hard
OL,7,Fto comprehend the loss of Jack and to
OL,8,Fmove on with our lives, as the memory
OL,9,Fand futility of what happened to Jack
OL,10,Fis still very raw and emotional."
OL,12,FLewes District Council, which brought
OL,13,Fthe prosecution, worked on the
OL,14,Finvestigation collaboratively with the
OL,15,FHealth and Safety Executive.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/12
