OL,3,CTravis Perkins fined #2m after dad-of-
OL,4,Cthree killed by timber-load lorry fall
OL,6,FCouncil deputy leader Christine
OL,7,FRobinson: "I hope our prosecution
OL,8,Fsends a strong message to businesses
OL,9,Fthat it is of the utmost importance
OL,10,Fthey adhere to health and safety
OL,11,Flegislation to ensure that something
OL,12,Flike this never happens again."
OL,14,FTravis Perkins was also ordered to pay
OL,15,F#85,000 in court costs.
